00:21:14.140 --> 00:21:17.770 align:middle line:10%
I had lymphoma, which had
started four years prior

00:21:17.770 --> 00:21:20.050 align:middle line:10%
with just a lump on my neck.

00:21:20.050 --> 00:21:24.010 align:middle line:84%
I had tumors, some of
them the size of lemons,

00:21:24.010 --> 00:21:29.230 align:middle line:84%
from the base of my skull, all
around my neck, under my arms,

00:21:29.230 --> 00:21:33.850 align:middle line:84%
into my chest, and all the
way down to my abdomen.

00:21:33.850 --> 00:21:37.690 align:middle line:84%
I was so weak that my organs
started shutting down one

00:21:37.690 --> 00:21:43.540 align:middle line:84%
by one, and I went into a coma,
and the doctors told my family

00:21:43.540 --> 00:21:45.190 align:middle line:90%
that these were my final hours.

00:21:45.190 --> 00:21:48.300 align:middle line:90%


00:21:48.300 --> 00:21:53.400 align:middle line:84%
I then went into a realm
where I became aware

00:21:53.400 --> 00:21:57.000 align:middle line:90%
of my deceased father.

00:21:57.000 --> 00:22:00.030 align:middle line:84%
When I was growing
up, my father and I

00:22:00.030 --> 00:22:03.810 align:middle line:84%
had a very turbulent
relationship.

00:22:03.810 --> 00:22:07.920 align:middle line:84%
I was always left with this
feeling that I had let him down

00:22:07.920 --> 00:22:10.200 align:middle line:84%
and that I had never
been the kind of daughter

00:22:10.200 --> 00:22:11.280 align:middle line:90%
he wanted me to be.

00:22:11.280 --> 00:22:14.470 align:middle line:90%


00:22:14.470 --> 00:22:18.850 align:middle line:84%
And here I was now with
him in the other realm,

00:22:18.850 --> 00:22:22.980 align:middle line:84%
and all I felt from
him and for him

00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:26.460 align:middle line:90%
was pure unconditional love.

00:22:26.460 --> 00:22:30.510 align:middle line:84%
There was no judgment from
him at all for anything

00:22:30.510 --> 00:22:33.090 align:middle line:90%
that I had done.

00:22:33.090 --> 00:22:39.030 align:middle line:84%
It was like I reached a state
of complete and total clarity.

00:22:39.030 --> 00:22:42.300 align:middle line:84%
And in that state of
clarity, I understood

00:22:42.300 --> 00:22:44.340 align:middle line:90%
why I had the cancer.

00:22:44.340 --> 00:22:49.410 align:middle line:84%
I understood how it was that
every decision and every choice

00:22:49.410 --> 00:22:53.550 align:middle line:84%
I had made in my life up to
that point was made from fear.

00:22:53.550 --> 00:22:56.580 align:middle line:90%


00:22:56.580 --> 00:23:00.330 align:middle line:10%
Now that I knew this
truth, I realized

00:23:00.330 --> 00:23:05.730 align:middle line:10%
that if I chose to go back
to my body that I would heal.

00:23:05.730 --> 00:23:09.000 align:middle line:84%
And it was in those
moments that I felt myself

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:11.130 align:middle line:90%
coming out of the coma.

00:23:11.130 --> 00:23:14.310 align:middle line:84%
By about a week, the
doctors could actually

00:23:14.310 --> 00:23:16.530 align:middle line:84%
see that the tumors
were dissolving

00:23:16.530 --> 00:23:20.250 align:middle line:84%
faster than they'd ever
seen tumors dissolve before.

00:23:20.250 --> 00:23:24.570 align:middle line:84%
At the end of five weeks,
I was physically stronger,

00:23:24.570 --> 00:23:28.080 align:middle line:84%
and they really could find no
trace of cancer in my body,

00:23:28.080 --> 00:23:31.200 align:middle line:84%
so they let me go home and
live my life cancer free.

00:23:31.200 --> 00:23:43.160 align:middle line:90%


00:23:43.160 --> 00:23:46.670 align:middle line:84%
>> Anita's story is the most
powerful example of just what

00:23:46.670 --> 00:23:49.040 align:middle line:90%
is possible with the human body.

00:23:49.040 --> 00:23:52.940 align:middle line:10%
She is proof that no matter
how far gone the body seems,

00:23:52.940 --> 00:23:56.060 align:middle line:10%
it is possible for tissues
to regenerate and function

00:23:56.060 --> 00:23:58.920 align:middle line:10%
to restore.

00:23:58.920 --> 00:24:00.810 align:middle line:84%
She had a dramatic
shift in the way

00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:04.200 align:middle line:84%
she looked at life from
one of fear to one of love.

00:24:04.200 --> 00:24:05.220 align:middle line:90%
That's it.

00:24:05.220 --> 00:24:08.070 align:middle line:84%
And her body
responded and healed.

00:24:08.070 --> 00:24:11.550 align:middle line:84%
But is she just some
random miracle or can

00:24:11.550 --> 00:24:13.980 align:middle line:84%
we study what happened
so that more people can

00:24:13.980 --> 00:24:14.780 align:middle line:90%
make this shift?

00:24:14.780 --> 00:24:18.198 align:middle line:90%


00:24:18.198 --> 00:24:20.740 align:middle line:10%
>> So I've been studying radical
remissions for over 10 years

00:24:20.740 --> 00:24:24.640 align:middle line:10%
now, and it started with a trip
around the world to interview

00:24:24.640 --> 00:24:27.610 align:middle line:10%
radical remission survivors
from all different countries.

00:24:27.610 --> 00:24:29.140 align:middle line:84%
And then, since
then, I've gone on

00:24:29.140 --> 00:24:31.510 align:middle line:84%
to analyze over
1,500 of these cases,

00:24:31.510 --> 00:24:34.550 align:middle line:84%
and I've conducted over
250 in-depth interviews.

00:24:34.550 --> 00:24:38.480 align:middle line:84%
And these are people
from all walks of life.

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:40.420 align:middle line:84%
So there have been
radical remissions

00:24:40.420 --> 00:24:43.270 align:middle line:84%
verified and reported for
every single cancer type--

00:24:43.270 --> 00:24:46.420 align:middle line:84%
people with pancreatic cancer,
with stage four lung cancer,

00:24:46.420 --> 00:24:49.240 align:middle line:84%
with a big brain tumor
that's considered inoperable.

00:24:49.240 --> 00:24:52.760 align:middle line:84%
There are examples of people out
there who have healed from it.

00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:54.970 align:middle line:84%
I've discovered over
75 different things

00:24:54.970 --> 00:24:57.460 align:middle line:84%
that these people have
done to try to get well,

00:24:57.460 --> 00:25:01.150 align:middle line:84%
but not everybody uses
all 75 of these factors.

00:25:01.150 --> 00:25:03.130 align:middle line:84%
However, when I
looked at the data,

00:25:03.130 --> 00:25:06.510 align:middle line:90%
they were all using these nine.

00:25:06.510 --> 00:25:09.770 align:middle line:90%
Only two of them are physical.

00:25:09.770 --> 00:25:12.530 align:middle line:84%
The rest are mental,
emotional, and spiritual.

00:25:12.530 --> 00:25:15.230 align:middle line:84%
And that hit me like
a ton of bricks.

00:25:15.230 --> 00:25:18.410 align:middle line:84%
There really is a way to
activate the immune system

00:25:18.410 --> 00:25:19.970 align:middle line:90%
with your mental-emotional work.

00:25:19.970 --> 00:25:22.250 align:middle line:10%
And of course, there's plenty
of science behind that.

00:25:22.250 --> 00:25:26.250 align:middle line:90%


00:25:26.250 --> 00:25:28.710 align:middle line:10%
Does that mean that we're
all going to heal tomorrow?

00:25:28.710 --> 00:25:31.500 align:middle line:84%
No, but it means they
deserve to be studied,

00:25:31.500 --> 00:25:34.140 align:middle line:84%
and there's something incredible
there for us to learn.

00:25:34.140 --> 00:25:37.360 align:middle line:90%


00:25:37.360 --> 00:25:40.780 align:middle line:84%
>> I very much believed that
perfect health was only one

00:25:40.780 --> 00:25:42.160 align:middle line:90%
prescription away.

00:25:42.160 --> 00:25:44.290 align:middle line:10%
And it wasn't until
about nine months

00:25:44.290 --> 00:25:49.450 align:middle line:10%
postpartum my pregnancy that
I got my first diagnosis.

00:25:49.450 --> 00:25:53.320 align:middle line:84%
And I was diagnosed with
