00:26:03.140 --> 00:26:05.770 align:middle line:84%
But of course, I was a new mom,
so it's easy to sort of dismiss

00:26:05.770 --> 00:26:07.780 align:middle line:90%
those symptoms.

00:26:07.780 --> 00:26:10.030 align:middle line:84%
And I had that
same feeling again,

00:26:10.030 --> 00:26:11.740 align:middle line:84%
like, I don't want
to take a medication

00:26:11.740 --> 00:26:12.790 align:middle line:90%
for the rest of my life.

00:26:12.790 --> 00:26:14.490 align:middle line:84%
There's got to be
a way out, right?

00:26:14.490 --> 00:26:16.460 align:middle line:84%
There's got to be
another option.

00:26:16.460 --> 00:26:20.320 align:middle line:84%
And so I went to a naturopath,
which was very unlike me.

00:26:20.320 --> 00:26:23.320 align:middle line:84%
I'd only ever been trained to
dismiss alternative medicine

00:26:23.320 --> 00:26:25.660 align:middle line:84%
as sort of this
nuisance, like a nuisance

00:26:25.660 --> 00:26:28.117 align:middle line:84%
to legitimate real
medicine, right?

00:26:28.117 --> 00:26:30.700 align:middle line:84%
And I went there because I knew
that conventional medicine had

00:26:30.700 --> 00:26:32.920 align:middle line:84%
nothing to offer me,
and I knew that there

00:26:32.920 --> 00:26:36.190 align:middle line:84%
was no way I would ever get
out of having a chronic illness

00:26:36.190 --> 00:26:38.980 align:middle line:84%
if I proceeded with my
conventional doctor.

00:26:38.980 --> 00:26:40.660 align:middle line:84%
So of course, I
put into remission

00:26:40.660 --> 00:26:45.460 align:middle line:84%
in six months what should be
a chronic lifelong disease.

00:26:45.460 --> 00:26:48.910 align:middle line:84%
And I experienced the raising
of a lot of red flags,

00:26:48.910 --> 00:26:51.100 align:middle line:84%
essentially, where
I said, you know,

00:26:51.100 --> 00:26:54.060 align:middle line:84%
I never learned that nutrition
has anything to do with health.

00:26:54.060 --> 00:27:00.300 align:middle line:90%


00:27:00.300 --> 00:27:01.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Now, open your little mouth.

00:27:01.620 --> 00:27:05.740 align:middle line:90%


00:27:05.740 --> 00:27:09.850 align:middle line:10%
>> We have a sick care system
where doctors and insurance

00:27:09.850 --> 00:27:13.330 align:middle line:10%
companies are basically treating
symptoms but aren't really

00:27:13.330 --> 00:27:16.540 align:middle line:10%
getting to root causes, in
many cases aren't dealing with

00:27:16.540 --> 00:27:17.800 align:middle line:10%
the whole person.

00:27:17.800 --> 00:27:20.470 align:middle line:10%
They're dealing with a
symptom, by which they then

00:27:20.470 --> 00:27:24.520 align:middle line:10%
give a drug, which
then has a side effect.

00:27:24.520 --> 00:27:27.070 align:middle line:90%
And so it keeps on spinning--

00:27:27.070 --> 00:27:32.200 align:middle line:84%
more toxicity, more toxicity,
more disease, more ill health.

00:27:32.200 --> 00:27:35.380 align:middle line:84%
>> Conventional medicine, tied
up in an old belief system,

00:27:35.380 --> 00:27:37.960 align:middle line:84%
is locked into the
cause of illness is tied

00:27:37.960 --> 00:27:40.300 align:middle line:84%
into our genetics
and our biochemistry.

00:27:40.300 --> 00:27:42.790 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, the
pharmaceutical industry

00:27:42.790 --> 00:27:43.970 align:middle line:90%
is the great savior.

00:27:43.970 --> 00:27:44.770 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:27:44.770 --> 00:27:46.690 align:middle line:84%
Because it will
make the chemistry

00:27:46.690 --> 00:27:48.730 align:middle line:84%
that should bring us
back to health again.

00:27:48.730 --> 00:27:51.380 align:middle line:84%
Well, it turns out
that's totally false.

00:27:51.380 --> 00:27:53.950 align:middle line:84%
There are so few diseases
that are actually organic.

00:27:53.950 --> 00:27:57.430 align:middle line:84%
In fact, 100% of
diabetes type 2 has

00:27:57.430 --> 00:27:59.740 align:middle line:84%
nothing to do with
genetics and everything

00:27:59.740 --> 00:28:00.790 align:middle line:90%
to do with lifestyle.

00:28:00.790 --> 00:28:03.040 align:middle line:84%
90% or more of
cardiovascular disease

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:05.850 align:middle line:84%
has nothing organically
wrong with the individual.

00:28:05.850 --> 00:28:08.550 align:middle line:84%
It's just the consequence
of dealing with stress.

