00:28:36.650 --> 00:28:37.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Medicine is useful.

00:28:37.910 --> 00:28:41.510 align:middle line:10%
Pharmaceutical medicine,
therapeutic interventions,

00:28:41.510 --> 00:28:43.710 align:middle line:10%
surgery, et cetera are useful.

00:28:43.710 --> 00:28:47.260 align:middle line:84%
I would say, maybe
10% acute illnesses.

00:28:47.260 --> 00:28:49.280 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, if you have
a chronic illness--

00:28:49.280 --> 00:28:51.440 align:middle line:84%
doesn't matter what it
is, cancer, heart disease,

00:28:51.440 --> 00:28:53.450 align:middle line:90%
