which means everything

00:28:56.390 --> 00:29:01.250 align:middle line:84%
from mind, body, emotions,
energy healing, even

00:29:01.250 --> 00:29:06.800 align:middle line:84%
distant healing, anything that
influences your experience

00:29:06.800 --> 00:29:08.315 align:middle line:90%
of mind, body, emotions.

00:29:08.315 --> 00:29:11.360 align:middle line:90%


00:29:11.360 --> 00:29:14.780 align:middle line:84%
>> So with emergencies and
acute illness like injury

