touching the environment.

00:46:21.610 --> 00:46:25.420 align:middle line:84%
It depends on the nervous
system to send information

00:46:25.420 --> 00:46:28.220 align:middle line:84%
about the environment
inside the body,

00:46:28.220 --> 00:46:29.800 align:middle line:84%
so the cells adjust
their biology

00:46:29.800 --> 00:46:31.690 align:middle line:84%
to match what's going
on in the world.

00:46:31.690 --> 00:46:34.780 align:middle line:84%
Well, we only have one problem
with that, and that is this--

00:46:34.780 --> 00:46:38.120 align:middle line:84%
consciousness is
an interpretation.

00:46:38.120 --> 00:46:43.890 align:middle line:10%
So my mind is interpreting
the environment.

00:46:43.890 --> 00:46:46.880 align:middle line:84%
So if I change my
perception, my mind,

00:46:46.880 --> 00:46:50.360 align:middle line:84%
change my belief about
life, I change the signals

00:46:50.360 --> 00:46:53.870 align:middle line:84%
that are going in and adjusting
the function of the cell.

00:46:53.870 --> 00:46:56.570 align:middle line:84%
The point is very,
very significant.

00:46:56.570 --> 00:47:00.290 align:middle line:84%
I, by my ability to
change my environment

00:47:00.290 --> 00:47:04.220 align:middle line:84%
and by my ability to change my
perception of the environment,

00:47:04.220 --> 00:47:06.800 align:middle line:84%
have the ability to control
my genetic activity.

00:47:06.800 --> 00:47:08.930 align:middle line:90%
I'm not a victim of my heredity.

00:47:08.930 --> 00:47:12.077 align:middle line:84%
I'm a master of my
genetic activity.

00:47:12.077 --> 00:47:14.938 align:middle line:90%


00:47:14.938 --> 00:47:16.980 align:middle line:84%
In understanding how we
deal with the environment

00:47:16.980 --> 00:47:18.810 align:middle line:84%
and deal with
perception, there is

00:47:18.810 --> 00:47:22.722 align:middle line:84%
a mind between the
environment and my cells.

00:47:22.722 --> 00:47:24.180 align:middle line:84%
And when I say "the
mind," everyone

00:47:24.180 --> 00:47:27.610 align:middle line:84%
thinks of a single
entity, "the mind."

00:47:27.610 --> 00:47:31.620 align:middle line:84%
The mind is comprised of two
interdependent elements that

00:47:31.620 --> 00:47:35.130 align:middle line:84%
work together, and
that's the conscious mind

00:47:35.130 --> 00:47:38.370 align:middle line:90%
and the subconscious mind.

00:47:38.370 --> 00:47:40.970 align:middle line:84%
The conscious mind, the
latest evolution of the brain,

00:47:40.970 --> 00:47:43.650 align:middle line:90%
is the creative mind.

00:47:43.650 --> 00:47:47.460 align:middle line:84%
When the conscious mind
is engaged in thinking,

00:47:47.460 --> 00:47:52.110 align:middle line:84%
the subconscious is the
default program, the autopilot.

00:47:52.110 --> 00:47:54.420 align:middle line:84%
So my conscious mind
could be engaged,

00:47:54.420 --> 00:47:57.180 align:middle line:84%
but my subconscious
mind will carry out

00:47:57.180 --> 00:48:00.690 align:middle line:84%
whatever chore I'm doing--
walking, driving the car,

00:48:00.690 --> 00:48:02.670 align:middle line:84%
communicating with
another person.

00:48:02.670 --> 00:48:04.440 align:middle line:84%
I don't need my
conscious mind for that.

00:48:04.440 --> 00:48:08.970 align:middle line:84%
