01:23:41.910 --> 01:23:43.800 align:middle line:84%
I just remember I could
hear my heartbeat.

01:23:43.800 --> 01:23:48.480 align:middle line:84%
It was like I could hear
water and air, [WHOOSHING]

01:23:48.480 --> 01:23:50.400 align:middle line:90%
really loud.

01:23:50.400 --> 01:23:52.480 align:middle line:90%
The fever kept going up.

01:23:52.480 --> 01:23:55.460 align:middle line:84%
And I kind of thought, oh,
I wonder if this is it.

01:23:55.460 --> 01:23:58.190 align:middle line:90%


01:23:58.190 --> 01:24:01.160 align:middle line:84%
When I woke up, my brother
was standing outside the glass

01:24:01.160 --> 01:24:02.420 align:middle line:90%
door with a laptop.

01:24:02.420 --> 01:24:04.880 align:middle line:84%
And he was telling me,
they're praying for you.

01:24:04.880 --> 01:24:07.910 align:middle line:84%
They did a group prayer on
Facebook with over 100 people.

01:24:07.910 --> 01:24:11.664 align:middle line:84%
And right after that,
I kind of came out.

01:24:11.664 --> 01:24:14.000 align:middle line:90%
That's pretty good.

01:24:14.000 --> 01:24:17.660 align:middle line:84%
>> How could my prayer,
how could my meditation,

01:24:17.660 --> 01:24:22.070 align:middle line:84%
how could my loving thoughts
of gratitude and appreciation

01:24:22.070 --> 01:24:27.620 align:middle line:84%
possibly impact the healing of
another person in the room with

01:24:27.620 --> 01:24:29.870 align:middle line:90%
me or halfway around the world?

01:24:29.870 --> 01:24:32.450 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is
that we are deeply

01:24:32.450 --> 01:24:36.650 align:middle line:84%
connected through a phenomenon
that is known as entanglement.

01:24:36.650 --> 01:24:40.220 align:middle line:84%
Entanglement is the term
in physics that tells us,

01:24:40.220 --> 01:24:46.850 align:middle line:84%
once something is unified, once
something begins as a whole,

01:24:46.850 --> 01:24:51.770 align:middle line:84%
even though it is separated
physically by many miles

01:24:51.770 --> 01:24:55.100 align:middle line:84%
or light years-- is what
they're finding in the cosmos--

01:24:55.100 --> 01:24:57.470 align:middle line:84%
energetically, everything's
still connected.

01:24:57.470 --> 01:24:59.100 align:middle line:90%
Why is that important?

01:24:59.100 --> 01:25:01.370 align:middle line:84%
Because if we go back
far enough in time,

01:25:01.370 --> 01:25:05.960 align:middle line:84%
there was a point in time
when you, me, and the Earth

01:25:05.960 --> 01:25:08.480 align:middle line:84%
were all connected
before what is

01:25:08.480 --> 01:25:11.780 align:middle line:84%
called the Big Bang, the
big release of energy.

01:25:11.780 --> 01:25:15.470 align:middle line:84%
When that happened, physically,
particles began to separate.

01:25:15.470 --> 01:25:18.410 align:middle line:84%
Energetically, the
particles remain connected.

01:25:18.410 --> 01:25:21.410 align:middle line:90%
We are part of this Earth.

01:25:21.410 --> 01:25:23.030 align:middle line:90%
And we are part of one another.

01:25:23.030 --> 01:25:25.130 align:middle line:84%
And that empowers
you and it empowers

01:25:25.130 --> 01:25:29.540 align:middle line:84%
me to participate in the
healing of our bodies

01:25:29.540 --> 01:25:32.360 align:middle line:84%
and those of our loved ones
in ways that science is only

01:25:32.360 --> 01:25:33.780 align:middle line:90%
beginning to understand.

01:25:33.780 --> 01:25:36.860 align:middle line:90%


01:25:36.860 --> 01:25:40.010 align:middle line:84%
>> So entanglement explain
scientifically how our prayers

01:25:40.010 --> 01:25:41.270 align:middle line:90%
might work.

01:25:41.270 --> 01:25:43.220 align:middle line:84%
But there's a whole
aspect of faith and prayer

01:25:43.220 --> 01:25:46.370 align:middle line:84%
that can't be explained
through science.

01:25:46.370 --> 01:25:48.350 align:middle line:84%
People travel all over
the world to holy sites

01:25:48.350 --> 01:25:51.340 align:middle line:84%
to receive energy
or faith healing.

01:25:51.340 --> 01:25:54.340 align:middle line:84%
Is it their unshakable belief
in God's power and therefore

01:25:54.340 --> 01:25:57.370 align:middle line:84%
