actual divine energy

01:25:59.470 --> 01:26:02.020 align:middle line:84%
that is causing
their transformation?

01:26:02.020 --> 01:26:04.810 align:middle line:84%
Either way, I'm fascinated
by the mystical.

01:26:04.810 --> 01:26:06.820 align:middle line:84%
And if faith healing
works for people,

01:26:06.820 --> 01:26:09.210 align:middle line:84%
why not respect the possibility
and keep an open mind?

