01:40:07.880 --> 01:40:10.080 align:middle line:90%
They died months later.

01:40:10.080 --> 01:40:12.590 align:middle line:90%
So many stories like that.

01:40:12.590 --> 01:40:16.778 align:middle line:84%
So I've been kind of
dreading this PET scan.

01:40:16.778 --> 01:40:18.320 align:middle line:84%
And also, I don't
like the radiation.

01:40:18.320 --> 01:40:21.930 align:middle line:90%
But you have to do it.

01:40:21.930 --> 01:40:26.410 align:middle line:84%
I actually was manifesting
a lot of pain in my body.

01:40:26.410 --> 01:40:29.340 align:middle line:84%
And then you can't tell whether
it's from the radiation damage

01:40:29.340 --> 01:40:31.450 align:middle line:90%
or what's going on.

01:40:31.450 --> 01:40:34.200 align:middle line:84%
But, yeah, it got to the
point where I thought

01:40:34.200 --> 01:40:37.740 align:middle line:90%
for sure it was coming back.

01:40:37.740 --> 01:40:40.260 align:middle line:84%
What seems very,
very clear to me

01:40:40.260 --> 01:40:43.740 align:middle line:84%
is that my body
wants to be healthy.

01:40:43.740 --> 01:40:45.300 align:middle line:90%
Our bodies want to be healthy.

01:40:45.300 --> 01:40:49.260 align:middle line:84%
But it's the head that just--
it's the fear and the this

01:40:49.260 --> 01:40:52.885 align:middle line:90%
and the whatever that wants to--

01:40:52.885 --> 01:40:56.520 align:middle line:84%
it's just like a racket you're
running on yourself, kind of,

01:40:56.520 --> 01:40:57.960 align:middle line:90%
and how to let go of that?

01:40:57.960 --> 01:41:04.850 align:middle line:90%


01:41:04.850 --> 01:41:07.790 align:middle line:84%
>> What is your one take-away
message that you want to share

01:41:07.790 --> 01:41:09.260 align:middle line:90%
with everybody?

01:41:09.260 --> 01:41:14.120 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I would say that
the most powerful moment,

01:41:14.120 --> 01:41:16.220 align:middle line:84%
the one where I had
the largest epiphany,

01:41:16.220 --> 01:41:21.450 align:middle line:84%
was toward the end of
the chemo and radiation.

01:41:21.450 --> 01:41:22.378 align:middle line:90%
I was really weak.

01:41:22.378 --> 01:41:24.670 align:middle line:84%
And I told my brother, I just
wanted to go to the beach

01:41:24.670 --> 01:41:25.920 align:middle line:90%
and I wanted to be in the sun.

01:41:25.920 --> 01:41:30.930 align:middle line:84%
So he carried me and
laid me in the grass.

01:41:30.930 --> 01:41:32.520 align:middle line:84%
And then he went
out on the beach.

01:41:32.520 --> 01:41:36.620 align:middle line:84%
And I was just laying
there, looking at everybody.

01:41:36.620 --> 01:41:39.470 align:middle line:84%
And I was watching people
rollerblade and bicycle

01:41:39.470 --> 01:41:42.955 align:middle line:84%
